data.description:
Come take a look at this charming three-bedroom, two bathroom home nestled at the peaceful dead-end street. Recently renovated, this property offers a blend of modern comfort and classic elegance, making it the ideal place to call home. 

Inside, the neutral color palette and the textured life-proof vinyl laminate flooring throughout the home provide a timeless backdrop for your personal style and decor. In addition to the renovations, this home is wired with fiber optic internet cables for fast internet and has a smart security system that controls locking and unlocking the doors, security cameras, turning on and off lights AND a smart thermostat! 

Don’t miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
